picod`\n299:   - Verification: `docker run --rm agentcube-test-picod which python3`\n300: \n301: ### Phase 8: Makefile Integration Tests (ST-8)\n302: \n303: - [ ] **T8.1**: Run make docker-build successfully\n304:   - Purpose: Verify Makefile target works\n305:   - File: `Makefile`\n306:   - Verification: `make docker-build IMAGE_REPO=test VERSION=test`\n307: \n308: - [ ] **T8.2**: Run make docker-build-router successfully\n309:   - Purpose: Verify Makefile target works\n310:   - File: `Makefile`\n311:   - Verification: `make docker-build-router IMAGE_REPO=test VERSION=test`\n312: \n313: - [ ] **T8.3**: Run make docker-build-picod successfully\n314:   - Purpose: Verify Makefile target works\n315:   - File: `Makefile`\n316:   - Verification: `make docker-build-picod IMAGE_REPO=test VERSION=test`\n317: \n318: - [ ] **T8.4**: Run make docker-build-all successfully\n319:   - Purpose: Verify aggregate target builds all images\n320:   - File: `Makefile`\n321:   - Verification: `make docker-build-all IMAGE_REPO=test VERSION=test`\n322: \n323: ---\n324: \n325: ## Task Dependencies\n326: \n327: ```\n328: Phase 1 (WorkloadManager Dockerfile) ───────────────────────────────────────────\n329: T1.1 (builder FROM) ──┬── T1.2 (go mod download + cache)\n330:                       ├── T1.3 (COPY source + CGO_ENABLED)\n331:                       ├── T1.4 (go build + ldflags)\n332:                       ├── T1.5 (runtime FROM alpine)\n333:                       ├── T1.6 (apk packages)\n334:                       ├── T1.7 (adduser apiserver)\n335:                       ├── T1.8 (COPY --from=builder)\n336:                       ├── T1.9 (USER + EXPOSE)\n337:                       └── T1.10 (ENTRYPOINT)\n338: \n339: Phase 2 (Router Dockerfile) ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n340: T2.1 (builder FROM) ──┬── T2.2 (go mod download + cache)\n341:                       ├── T2.3 (COPY client-go/)\n342:                       ├── T2.4 (CGO + go build)\n343:                 