" docker/Dockerfile.picod | grep \"2\"` |\n386: | Phase 4 | `grep \"docker-build-all:\" Makefile` |\n387: | Phase 5 | `grep \"CGO_ENABLED=0\" docker/Dockerfile docker/Dockerfile.router docker/Dockerfile.picod` |\n388: | Phase 6 | `docker build -f docker/Dockerfile -t test-workloadmanager . && docker image inspect test-workloadmanager --format='{{.Size}}'` |\n389: | Phase 7 | `docker run --rm test-workloadmanager id -u | grep \"1000\"` |\n390: | Phase 8 | `make docker-build-all IMAGE_REPO=test VERSION=test` |\n391: \n392: ---\n393: \n394: ## Acceptance Criteria\n395: \n396: - [ ] WorkloadManager Dockerfile has 2-stage build structure\n397: - [ ] Router Dockerfile has 2-stage build structure\n398: - [ ] PicoD Dockerfile has 2-stage build structure\n399: - [ ] WorkloadManager uses golang:1.24-alpine builder + alpine:3.19 runtime\n400: - [ ] Router uses golang:1.24-alpine builder + alpine:3.19 runtime\n401: - [ ] PicoD uses golang:1.24 builder + ubuntu:24.04 runtime\n402: - [ ] WorkloadManager runs as UID 1000 (non-root)\n403: - [ ] Router runs as UID 1000 (non-root)\n404: - [ ] PicoD runs as root (UID 0)\n405: - [ ] All Dockerfiles have CGO_ENABLED=0\n406: - [ ] All Dockerfiles have ldflags=\"-w -s\" optimization\n407: - [ ] WorkloadManager/Router use BuildKit cache mounts for go mod/go build\n408: - [ ] Router Dockerfile includes client-go/ COPY\n409: - [ ] PicoD Dockerfile installs python3, python3-pip\n410: - [ ] WorkloadManager image size <50MB\n411: - [ ] Router image size <50MB\n412: - [ ] PicoD image size <100MB\n413: - [ ] Makefile has docker-build target\n414: - [ ] Makefile has docker-build-router target\n415: - [ ] Makefile has docker-build-picod target\n416: - [ ] Makefile has docker-build-all target\n417: - [ ] Makefile has docker-buildx-push targets for multi-arch\n418: - [ ] Runtime images have no Go toolchain\n419: - [ ] Runtime images have no Go source files\n420: - [ ] All images build successfully with make docker-build-all\n421: \n422: ---\n423: \n424: ## File Changes Summary\n425: \n426: | File | Action | Lines | Description |\n427: |------|--------|-------|-------------|\n428: | `docker/Dockerfile` | Create | 25 | WorkloadManager multi-stage build (builder → runtime) |\n429: | `docker/Dockerfile.router` | Create | 30 | Router multi-stage build (builder → runtime with client-go) |\n430: | `docker/Dockerfile.picod` | Create | 25 | PicoD multi-stage build (builder → Ubuntu runtime) |\n431: | `Makefile` | Modify | 35 | Add docker-build, docker-build-router, docker-build-picod, docker-build-all, docker-buildx-push targets |\n432: \n433: ---\n434: \n435: ## Implementation Notes\n436: \n437: ### Multi-Stage Build Pattern\n438: \n439: ```dockerfile\n440: # Stage 1: Builder\n441: FROM golang:1.24-alpine AS builder\n442: WORKDIR /app\n443: COPY go.mod go.sum ./\n444: RUN --mount=type=cache,target=/go/pkg/mod go mod download\n445: COPY . .\n446: ENV CGO_ENABLED=0\n447: RUN --mount=type=cache,target=/root/.cache/go-build \\\n448:     go build -ldflags=\"-w -s\" -o /app/bin/<binary> ./cmd/<module>\n449: \n450: # Stage 2: Runtime\n451: FROM alpine:3.19\n452: RUN apk add --no-cache ca-certificates tzdata\n453: RUN adduser -D -u 1000 <user>\n454: WORKDIR /app\n455: COPY --from=builder /app/bin/<binary> /app/bin/<binary>\n456: USER 1000\n457: EXPOSE 8080\n458: ENTRYPOINT [\" /app/bin/<binary>\"]\n459: ```\n460: \n461: ### BuildKit Cache Optimization\n462: \n463: | Cache Mount | Target | Purpose |\n464: |-------------|--------|---------|\n465: | `/go/pkg/mod` | Module cache | Persist module downloads across builds |\n466: | `/root/.cache/go-build` | Build cache | Cache compiled artifacts |\n467: \n468: ### Binary Size Optimization Flags\n469: \n470: | Flag | Effect |\n471: |------|--------|\n472: | `-w` | Strip DWARF debug information |\n473: | `-s` | Strip symbol table |\n474: | `CGO_ENABLED=0` | Static-like compilation |\n475: \n476: ### User Security Context\n477: \n478: | Image | User | Reason |\n479: |-------|------|--------|\n480: | WorkloadManager | UID 1000 | Non-root for security |\n481: | Router | UID 1000 | Non-root for security |\n482: | PicoD | root (UID 0) | Sandbox pod management requires elevated privileges |\n483: \n484: ---\n485: \n486: ## Implementation Timeline\n487: \n488: | Phase | Tasks | Status | Completion |\n489: |-------|-------|--------|------------|\n490: | Phase 1: WorkloadManager Dockerfile | T1.1-T1.10 | Pending | 0% |\n491: | Phase 2: Router Dockerfile | T2.1-T2.8 | Pending | 0% |\n492: | Phase 3: PicoD Dockerfile | T3.1-T3.7 | Pending | 0% |\n493: | Phase 4: Makefile Targets | T4.1-T4.5 | Pending | 0% |\n494: | Phase 5: Syntax Validation | T5.1-T5.9 | Pending | 0% |\n495: | Phase 6: Build Execution | T6.1-T6.6 | Pending | 0% |\n496: | Phase 7: Runtime Verification | T7.1-T7.9 | Pending | 0% |\n497: | Phase 8: Makefile Integration | T8.1-T8.4 | Pending | 0% |\n498: \n499: **Total Progress: 0% Complete (0/46 tasks)**\n500: \n501: ---\n502: \n503: ## References\n504: \n505: - Design: `changes/AR-032/design.md`\n506: - Delta Spec: `changes/AR-032/delta-spec.md`\n507: - Proposal: `changes/AR-032/proposal.md`\n508: - Docker multi-stage builds: https://docs.docker.com/build/building/multi-stage/\n509: - BuildKit cache mounts: https://docs.docker.com/build/buildkit/#cache-mounts\n510: - Go cross-compilation: https://go.dev/doc/install/source#environment\n\n(End of file - total 510 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-032 — Dockerfile 多阶段构建 Tasks\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-032 — Dockerfile 多阶段构建 (3 images) |\n| Module | `docker` |\n| Language | Dockerfile |\n| Size | S |\n| Design | [Stage ST-3 completed] |\n\n---\n\n## Task Checklist\n\n### Phase 1: WorkloadManager Dockerfile Foundation (ST-1)\n\n- [ ] **T1.1**: Create builder stage with golang:1.24-alpine base\n  - Purpose: Define builder stage for Go compilation","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260